    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2001-12-20", 
    "text": "Twenty-First Century Water Policy Commission Establishment Act - Establishes the Twenty-First Century Water Policy Commission to: (1) study all aspects of water management by Federal, State, and local agencies and by private sector entities; and (2) develop recommendations for a specified comprehensive water policy."
